mo_imbEShPrxqIw">Tần trung ngâm kỳ 08 - Ngũ huyền - 秦中吟其八－五弦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-Thai-th%E1%BA%A1ch-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BA%ADu-quan-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-Vqow27pdQlBUwaSkG3-PNQ">Thiên Thai thạch lương hậu quan bộc bố - 天台石梁雨後觀瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-zQyjfkM-l-eVSsp11IFYtg">Nguỵ Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/%E1%BB%A8c-T%E1%BA%A7n-Nga-T%E1%BB%AD-D%E1%BA%A1-ca/poem-_hs7FR3fe5rQ_i1JDQVkEg">Ức Tần Nga - Tử Dạ ca - 憶秦娥－子夜歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%BA/author-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Hạ Chú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/V%C3%A3n/poem-hcrRzsxpWnVU7pmPv8so3A">Vãn - 晚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
